NK015(ba)011:0: ma y+aa sh+ai ba ma h+aa dza y+aa s+ya sh+ai r+sha ma //
NK015(ba)011:2: / sgyu 'phrul zhi ba d+r+wa chen gyi dabu'o //
NK015(ba)011:4: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje dbang chen la //
NK015(ba)011:5: kun nas dwang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)011:6: rten gyi gang zag shes rab mchog dang ldan pas /
NK015(ba)011:7: phyi nang gi dam tshig rnams ma nyams la yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK015(ba)011:8: dbang thams cad kyi rgyal sar chud pa /
NK015(ba)011:9: shes rab thams cad kyi rtsal dang ldan zhing /
NK015(ba)011:10: brtson 'grus kyi go cha bgos pa zhig gis /
NK015(ba)011:11: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas kyis mngon sum du bya bar 'dod pas /
NK015(ba)011:12: sku gsum lhun gyi grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bya ste /
NK015(ba)011:13: de la'ang rnam pa gnyis te /
NK015(ba)011:14: ma bsgyur rnal ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)011:15: bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)011:16: ma bsgyur rnal ma'i dkyil 'khor la bzhi ste /
NK015(ba)011:17: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK015(ba)011:18: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK015(ba)011:20: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK015(ba)011:21: de la dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)011:23: bsam gtan gyi phyag rgya lngas /
NK015(ba)011:24: lus sems tshags su stsal te /
NK015(ba)011:25: bsam gtan la mnyam par bzhag pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:27: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK015(ba)011:28: rtogs pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK015(ba)011:30: phyi nang gi chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK015(ba)011:31: chos kyi dbyings sems kyi de kho na nyid du rig pas nyams su myong bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:32: de ni chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:33: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)011:34: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK015(ba)011:35: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK015(ba)011:37: de ltar chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par //
NK015(ba)011:38: de ma rtogs pa'i sems can gyis khyab /
NK015(ba)011:39: sems can gyis gar khyab par /
NK015(ba)011:40: rnal 'byor pa'i rtogs pa'i byin rlabs kyi snying rjes khyab ste /
NK015(ba)011:41: de ltar rnal 'byor pa'i rig pa khyab bdal du gsal ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:42: de ma rtogs pa'i sems can gyi khams chos kyi dbyings nyid las snang ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:43: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:44: de nas rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la don rnam pa gnyis kyi bstan te /
NK015(ba)011:45: ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK015(ba)011:46: phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin la thugs kyi sgrib pa sbyang ba'o //
NK015(ba)011:47: de la rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK015(ba)011:48: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK015(ba)011:50: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge a dkar po bsgom par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:51: phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin la thugs kyi sgrib pa sbyang ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:52: a dkar rab tu brten gyur las //
NK015(ba)011:53: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spros //
NK015(ba)011:56: a dkar po de la brten nas /
NK015(ba)011:57: de la a dkar po gcig spros /
NK015(ba)011:58: de la brten nas gnyis spros /
NK015(ba)011:59: de la brten nas bzhi spros te /
NK015(ba)011:60: de bzhin du je mang je mang /
NK015(ba)011:61: je ring je ring du spros te /
NK015(ba)011:62: gzhugs sems kyi khyab tshad kyi a dkar po yungs 'bru tsam gyis gang nas /
NK015(ba)011:64: slar 'od zer tshur 'dus kyang gzhi po'i a ma 'phel /
NK015(ba)011:65: phyir a mang po spros kyang gzhi bo'i a ma 'grib /
NK015(ba)011:66: de byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid yin par shes par bya /
NK015(ba)011:67: yi ge gzhan gang spro na yang /
NK015(ba)011:68: tshul de bzhin du shes par bya /
NK015(ba)011:69: 'di man chad yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK015(ba)011:70: bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul la gnyis te /
NK015(ba)011:72: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:73: de la rten bskyed pa la gnyis kyi dang po 'og gzhi bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:74: a las e yam bam lam sum ram rnams spros pa las /
NK015(ba)011:75: e las chos 'byung grum gsum mthing ka rgya khyon nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK015(ba)011:76: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa /
NK015(ba)011:77: kha dog dud kha dbyibs zla gam du gyur par bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:78: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar la zlum pa /
NK015(ba)011:79: tha ma bum pas mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)011:80: de'i steng du lam las gser gyi sa gzhi gru bzhi ser po /
NK015(ba)011:81: tha ma bum pa rdo rjes mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)011:82: de'i steng du sum las rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa ri'i rgyal po ri rab /
NK015(ba)011:83: dbyibs gru bzhi pa kha khyer dang rgya mnyam pa /
NK015(ba)011:84: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor du gyur te /
NK015(ba)011:85: phyed mar 'phros pas 'og gi 'byung ba rnams cha snyoms /
NK015(ba)011:86: phyed ri rab kyi kha rgyan du me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur par bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:87: h'u mar 'phros te rdo rje rgya gram du gyur /
NK015(ba)011:89: rgya gram rdo rje'i gur zlum por gyur par bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:90: gdam ngag gi bar 'dir sna tshogs rdo rje las gur khang gzhung bzhin du bya gsung /
NK015(ba)011:91: de nas bzhugs gnas bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:94: zhes skabs 'dir h'u las sna tshogs rdo rje rgya
NK015(ba)011:95: gram las gur khang du bsgom pa man ngag gi
NK015(ba)011:100: rin po che sna lnga las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK015(ba)011:101: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin rgya chad pa med pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:102: rgya khyon tshad bzung du med pa /
NK015(ba)011:103: shar dkar po 'khor los brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:104: lho ser po rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:105: nub dmar po pad+mas brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:106: byang ljang gu ral gris brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:107: steng mthing ka rdo rjes brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:108: mu tig gi d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pas brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:109: ka rgyan dang ka zhu thams cad rin po che 'bar ba la byas pa /
NK015(ba)011:110: ta ra na yis bzung ba /
NK015(ba)011:111: nyi ma dang zla ba phyed pa /
NK015(ba)011:112: rang sa'i skar khung lding pa /
NK015(ba)011:113: rnga yab dang rnga yab chen po'i bsil yang du 'phyo ba /
NK015(ba)011:114: dril bu dang dril bu chen po'i sgra 'khrol ba /
NK015(ba)011:115: kun tu bzang po'i thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes la /
NK015(ba)011:116: 'dod spyod rnam pa lngar snang zhing /
NK015(ba)011:117: de yang chos nyid kyi rgyan du rig pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:118: gzugs sdug pa sna tshogs dang /
NK015(ba)011:119: sgra snyan pa sna tshogs dang /
NK015(ba)011:120: dri zhim pa sna tshogs dang /
NK015(ba)011:121: ro mngar ba sna tshogs dang /
NK015(ba)011:122: reg bya 'jam pa sna tshogs nam mkha' la sprin bzhin du 'khrigs pa /
NK015(ba)011:123: bar snang la char bzhin du 'bab pa /
NK015(ba)011:124: sa gzhi la rtsi shing bzhin du skyes te /
NK015(ba)011:125: ling long byed par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)011:126: gzhan yang de'i phyi rol na /
NK015(ba)011:127: ta la'i phreng ba gser gyi tsong tsong gis sbrel ba /
NK015(ba)011:128: dpag bsam gyi shing gser gyi tsong tsong gis bres pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:129: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rdzing bu bdud rtsis
NK015(ba)011:130: gang ba rnams kyi thams cad du khyab par bsgom
NK015(ba)011:131: mo // gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing ka la /
NK015(ba)011:132: rtsibs bzhi ser po byung ba'i rtsibs mchan sngon po /
NK015(ba)011:133: de'i phyi rol mu khyud rdo rje rwa bas brgyan pa la /
NK015(ba)011:134: rdo rje'i ka ba brgyad zug pa /
NK015(ba)011:135: de'i phyi rol gru chad bzhi dang /
NK015(ba)011:136: glo 'bur mkhar thabs bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)011:137: de'i phyi rol lha snam sgo bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:138: de nas gdan bting ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:139: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK015(ba)011:140: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK015(ba)011:141: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK015(ba)011:142: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK015(ba)011:144: dbus su mi 'jigs pa bzhi'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:145: seng ge brgyad kyi khri byung bar gyur to //
NK015(ba)011:146: shar du stobs bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:147: glang po che brgyad kyi khri byung /
NK015(ba)011:148: lhor rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:150: nub tu dbang bcu'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:151: rma bya brgyad kyi khri byung /
NK015(ba)011:152: byang du phrin las bzhi'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:153: shang shang brgyad kyi khri byung /
NK015(ba)011:154: de dag gi bar mtshams su /
NK015(ba)011:155: rin po che'i khri ka bas brgyan pa la /
NK015(ba)011:156: rin po che'i khri'i steng na mu tig gi d+r+wa bas g.yog pa /
NK015(ba)011:157: de'i steng du pad+ma 'dab ma stong dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)011:160: rtsibs mchan bzhi gru chad bzhi dang brgyad la /
NK015(ba)011:161: rin po che'i khri'i steng nyi zla pad+ma gsum brtsegs dang ldan pa re re /
NK015(ba)011:163: sgo bzhir bdud bzhi'i steng du nyi ma'o //
NK015(ba)011:165: da ni brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)011:167: thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK015(ba)011:169: dang po gsung gi cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)011:170: a dkar po las k+sha sngon po byung /
NK015(ba)011:171: a dang k+sha'i khyad par las /
NK015(ba)011:172: yi ge bzhi bcu gnyis byung ste /
NK015(ba)011:173: dbus su tha sngon po gnyis /
NK015(ba)011:174: shar du ha dkar po gnyis /
NK015(ba)011:176: nub tu d+ha dmar po gnyis /
NK015(ba)011:177: byang du na ljang gu gnyis /
NK015(ba)011:179: lho nub tu kha dang tsha /
NK015(ba)011:180: nub byang du ga dang dza /
NK015(ba)011:181: byang shar du g+ha dang dz+ha /
NK015(ba)011:182: shar lho'i gru chad la pa dang ya /
NK015(ba)011:183: lho nub kyi gru chad la pha dang wa /
NK015(ba)011:184: nub byang gi gru chad la ba dang ra /
NK015(ba)011:185: byang shar gyi gru cha da la b+ha dang la /
NK015(ba)011:200: 'gro ba sems can gyi ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)011:202: thugs kyi cho 'phrul du gyur te /
NK015(ba)011:203: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)011:204: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)011:205: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)011:206: nub tu pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)011:207: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)011:208: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan du rin po che'i myu gu dang me long /
NK015(ba)011:209: lho nub tu ral gri dang rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK015(ba)011:210: nub byang du pad+ma dkar po dang pi wam /
NK015(ba)011:211: byang shar du rdo rje dang gar gyi lag pa /
NK015(ba)011:213: shar lho'i gru chad la klu shing bdug spos /
NK015(ba)011:214: lho nub tu chos kyi 'khor lo dang me tog gi phreng ba /
NK015(ba)011:215: nub byang du rin po che'i snye ma dang mar me /
NK015(ba)011:216: byang shar du ut+pala dang dri chab /
NK015(ba)011:217: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK015(ba)011:218: lho sgor rdo rje'i dbyug pa dang zhags pa /
NK015(ba)011:219: nub sgor pad+ma'i dbyug pa dang lcags sgrog /
NK015(ba)011:220: byang sgor rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyug pa dang dril bu /
NK015(ba)011:221: shar stod du rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa /
NK015(ba)011:224: lho smad du sreg shang dang par bu /
NK015(ba)011:226: nub smad du chos kyi glegs bam /
NK015(ba)011:227: byang stod du rin po che /
NK015(ba)011:228: byang smad du me chu gnyis /
NK015(ba)011:229: de rnams la 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)011:230: 'phags pa'i thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK015(ba)011:231: sems can gyi yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)011:232: slar 'dus pa las sku phra mor gyur /
NK015(ba)011:233: sku phra mo las sku phra mo spros pas /
NK015(ba)011:235: sems can gyi lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)011:236: slar 'dus sku phra mo la thims pa las /
NK015(ba)011:237: sku phyag rgya'i cho 'phrul du bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:242: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:243: sku mdog mthing ka zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK015(ba)011:246: dbu ral pa'i thor tshugs nag po 'gying ba /
NK015(ba)011:247: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnam ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)011:249: tha ma na rin po che /
NK015(ba)011:252: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)011:253: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)011:254: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK015(ba)011:255: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)011:256: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma sku mdog yab dang mthun pa /
NK015(ba)011:257: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK015(ba)011:258: g.yon pas dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:262: shar du rnam par snang mdzad me long lta bu'i ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:263: sku mdog dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas sngo /
NK015(ba)011:265: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams te yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)011:266: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK015(ba)011:267: tha ma na rin po che /
NK015(ba)011:274: lho phyogs su rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK015(ba)011:275: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:276: sku mdog ser po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK015(ba)011:278: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)011:279: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK015(ba)011:287: snang ba mtha' yas so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:288: sku mdog dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK015(ba)011:291: phyag dang po gnyis pad+ma dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)011:292: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK015(ba)011:294: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK015(ba)011:299: byang du don yod grub pa /
NK015(ba)011:300: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:303: zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba /
NK015(ba)011:304: phyag dang po gnyis ral gri dang dril bu bsnams te yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)011:305: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK015(ba)011:307: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK015(ba)011:309: phyag mtshan de dag la ni ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)011:310: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag thams cad ral pa'i thor tshugs nag po 'gying ba /
NK015(ba)011:311: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)011:312: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyis /
NK015(ba)011:313: skyil mo krung gis rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)011:314: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK015(ba)011:315: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK015(ba)011:317: yab yum bcu po de rnams ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin te /
NK015(ba)011:318: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:319: yab yum zhal sbyor du gnas shing /
NK015(ba)011:320: spyan yang gcig gis gcig la gzigs /
NK015(ba)011:321: yang rnam pa gcig tu na /
NK015(ba)011:322: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyang 'byung ba lnga chos kyi dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:323: yab thams cad yum la gzigs /
NK015(ba)011:324: chos kyi dbyings nyid phung po lnga sogs /
NK015(ba)011:325: chos thams cad bkag pa med par shar ba'i dus na /
NK015(ba)011:326: 'jug ma'i srin bu yan chad phung po lngar 'dus shing /
NK015(ba)011:327: de dag thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i mkhyen pa'i
NK015(ba)011:328: ye shes khyab bdal med par shar ba'i rtags su
NK015(ba)011:329: / yum thams cad la gzigs so //
NK015(ba)011:330: de dag thams cad dbyer med pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:331: yab yum thams cad zhal sbyor du gnas so //
NK015(ba)011:332: de nas sems dpa' yab yum bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:334: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK015(ba)011:336: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la sa'i snying po yab yum sku mdog dkar po /
NK015(ba)011:337: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab kyi phyag g.yas na /
NK015(ba)011:340: yang na dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:341: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis me long bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:342: zhabs gnyis phyed krung du bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)011:343: yab yum zhal sbyor du gnas pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:344: yab yum de gnyis ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnam
NK015(ba)011:345: par snang mdzad kyi sku dang thugs las byung ba'o
NK015(ba)011:347: t+r+aam ma l+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam ho /
NK015(ba)011:349: lho nub kyi rtsibs mchan la nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK015(ba)011:350: yum rin po che'i phreng ba ma /
NK015(ba)011:351: sku mdog ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK015(ba)011:352: yab kyi phyag g.yas na ral gri /
NK015(ba)011:353: yum gyi phyag na rin po che'i phreng ba bsnams te /
NK015(ba)011:354: yab kyi dbu thod bcings pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:355: h+r+aihh+aa h'u pad+ma b+ha ta ma /
NK015(ba)011:358: nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la spyan gzigs ras dbang phyug dang /
NK015(ba)011:359: lha mo dbyangs mkhan ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK015(ba)011:360: yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma dkar po bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:361: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis chos kyi pi wam btegs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:362: dzim ku ru p+aa ni h+r+aih a nirti r+aa ga ya mi /
NK015(ba)011:364: byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la /
NK015(ba)011:368: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:369: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis gar gyi lag pa bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)011:370: zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa yab kyi zhal du stobs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:371: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:375: byams pa dang bdug spos ma sku mdog dkar mo /
NK015(ba)011:376: yab kyi phyag na klu shing dang g+han+d+he bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:377: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis bdug spos bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:378: th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:381: lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:382: lha mo me tog ma sku mdog ser po /
NK015(ba)011:383: yab kyi phyag g.yas na chos kyi 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:384: yum gyi phyag na me tog gi phreng ba bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:385: h'u swa r+aa tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:386: bam d+ai ba su ki n+ai /
NK015(ba)011:388: nub byang gi gru chad la kun tu bzang po dang /
NK015(ba)011:389: lha mo mar me gnyis sku mdog dmar mo /
NK015(ba)011:390: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i snye ma bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:391: yum gyi phyag na mar me bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:392: m+aum sh+r+ai a ram g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:395: byang shar gyi gru chad la 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:396: lha mo dri cha ba ma sku mdog ljang ku /
NK015(ba)011:397: yab kyi phyag g.yas na ut+pala bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:398: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi dri chab bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:399: sems dpa' yab yum de rnams ni /
NK015(ba)011:400: kun kyang dbu ral pa'i thor tshugs mnga' ba /
NK015(ba)011:401: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK015(ba)011:402: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)011:403: zhabs thams cad phyed krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)011:404: yab yum thams cad zhal sbyor du gnas te /
NK015(ba)011:405: thugs rjes sems can thams cad la bu gcig la mas byams pa bzhin du sems pa ste /
NK015(ba)011:407: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK015(ba)011:411: shar stod du bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phyed pa
NK015(ba)011:412: po yid kun tu bzang po sku mdog sngon po
NK015(ba)011:414: phyag gnyis mnyam pa'i phyag rgya'i dkyil na /
NK015(ba)011:415: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa las ye shes kyi 'od zer 'phro ba /
NK015(ba)011:416: zhabs mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung gi pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)011:417: a a a badz+ra b+ha dra sa m+aan+ta /
NK015(ba)011:420: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams cad gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:422: shes bya'i bag chags dag pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:423: sku mdog dkar mo phyag gnyis chos 'byung gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK015(ba)011:424: gdan pad+ma'i steng du zhabs mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)011:425: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku yin te /
NK015(ba)011:426: dbyings mkhyen pa dang ldan pa'i rtags su yum gyi zhal shar du gzigs pa /
NK015(ba)011:427: mkhyen pa'i ye shes shes bya'i dngos po thams cad dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:428: yab kyi zhal nub tu gzigs so //
NK015(ba)011:431: shar smad du lha'i thub pa dbang po brgya byin sku mdog dkar po /
NK015(ba)011:432: phyag na pi wang bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:433: 'khor lha dmag 'bum dang bcas pa shar smad du bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:436: lho stod du lha ma yin gyi thub pa dpa' brjid go cha can /
NK015(ba)011:437: sku mdog ljang nag khros pa'i cha byad can /
NK015(ba)011:440: mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:442: lho smad du mi yi thub pa sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu /
NK015(ba)011:444: g.yon na bar bu bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:447: nub smad du byol song gi thub pa /
NK015(ba)011:448: seng ge dam brtan gser gyi kha dog dan /
NK015(ba)011:449: spyi bor chos kyi glegs bam khur ba /
NK015(ba)011:450: byong song gi khams kyi ma rig pa'i mun khang 'byed par bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:453: byang stod du yi dwags kyi thub pa kha 'bar ma bud med kyi gzugs can /
NK015(ba)011:454: sku mdog ljang ser du 'dug pa /
NK015(ba)011:455: skra dang sma ra khams pa sen mo ring ba /
NK015(ba)011:456: phyag na rin po che'i za ma tog bsnams pa'i nang nas /
NK015(ba)011:457: yi dwags thams cad la mchod sbyin gtor bar bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)011:460: byang smad du dmyal ba'i thub pa sku mdog nag po /
NK015(ba)011:462: phyag g.yas na mi bsnams te grang ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar byed pa /
NK015(ba)011:463: g.yon na chu bsnams te tsha ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar byed par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)011:464: thub pa de rnams ni sprul pa'i sku yin te /
NK015(ba)011:465: 'gro ba'i don la thugs bsnyel ba mi mnga' bar don mdzad pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)011:468: thub drug kun dge slong gi cha byad can du bzheng /
NK015(ba)011:484: shar lhor lha la lho phyogs mi //
NK015(ba)011:485: lho nub nub byang yi dwags byol //
NK015(ba)011:486: byang dang byang shar lha min dmyal //
NK015(ba)011:489: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:491: shar sgor khro bo gshin rje dang yum rdo rje
NK015(ba)011:492: lcags kyu ma gnyis sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig
NK015(ba)011:493: phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa
NK015(ba)011:494: / yab kyi phyag g.yas na thod dbyug g.yon thod khrag /
NK015(ba)011:495: yum gyi g.yas na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:497: dpal gyi chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:498: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs par bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:500: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:502: lho sgor khro bo stobs po che dang /
NK015(ba)011:503: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog ser nag /
NK015(ba)011:504: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje'i dbyug pa /
NK015(ba)011:506: yum gyi g.yas na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:507: 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:509: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti sh+aa ri dz+wa la n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:511: nub sgor khro bo rta mgrin dang /
NK015(ba)011:512: yum rdo rje lcags sgrog ma gnyis sku mdog dmar nag /
NK015(ba)011:513: yab kyi g.yas na pad+ma'i dbyug pa sbrul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:515: yum gyi phyag g.yas na lcags sgrog bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)011:516: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:517: h'u big+n+aana ta kri ta phata /
NK015(ba)011:518: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:519: byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:520: yum rdo rje dril bu ma gnyis sku mdog ljang nag /
NK015(ba)011:521: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyug pa /
NK015(ba)011:523: yum gyi g.yas na gser gyi dril chen 'khrol ba /
NK015(ba)011:524: lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:525: khro bo ya yum de rnams ni rdo rje'i sku yin te /
NK015(ba)011:526: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK015(ba)011:527: chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)011:528: g.yon thams cad thod pa khrag gi bkang ba thogs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:529: gzhal yas khang thams cad kyang khro bo de dag gi me dpung gi 'khrigs te /
NK015(ba)011:530: me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor na bde bar gshegs pa rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:531: bdag gi dkyil 'khor 'di na gnas pa bzhin du /
NK015(ba)011:532: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i chos kyi dbyings kyi
NK015(ba)011:533: gar khyab pa de dag thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK015(ba)011:534: 'khor gyis khyab / rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis gar khyab pa de yang /
NK015(ba)011:535: chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab pa shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:536: de ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhis
NK015(ba)011:537: bstan pa'i dang po bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul de song
NK015(ba)011:538: / yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)011:539: don ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK015(ba)011:540: rtags rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa'i dbang ngo //
NK015(ba)011:542: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:544: chos thams cad don dam rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de
NK015(ba)011:545: dag chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa chen po'i rang bzhin
NK015(ba)011:546: la g.yos pa med par rtogs pa ni don gyi
NK015(ba)011:547: dbang ngo // rtags kyi dbang ni /
NK015(ba)011:548: rgyal ba de dag gi spyi gtsug tu mi bskyod
NK015(ba)011:549: pa sku mdog sngon po re res dbu brgyan par
NK015(ba)011:550: bya'o // ma h+aa +aa d+aar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:552: don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag thams cad kyang /
NK015(ba)011:553: chos kyi dbyings la 'gag pa med pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK015(ba)011:554: rtags rgyal ba de dag gi dpral bar rnam par
NK015(ba)011:555: snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po re re bsgom par
NK015(ba)011:556: bya'o // ma h+aa sa m+aan+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:558: don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma 'gag par snang ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:559: ngo bo chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa gnyis ye nas dbyer med par shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:560: rtag rna ltag g.yas su rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK015(ba)011:561: sku mdog ser po re re bsgom par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:562: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:564: rgyal ba de dag kyang gdul bya tha dad la mos pa 'byung bar shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:566: ltag pa'i steng du snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po re re bsgom par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:567: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+tana dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:569: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du ma 'gags par snang ba ni gzhan don no //
NK015(ba)011:570: ngo bo ma skyes pa ni bdag don te /
NK015(ba)011:571: de gnyis dus gcig pa ni don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:573: rna ltag g.yon pa'i steng du don yod grub pa re re bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)011:574: rgyal ba de rnams kyi dbu la rin po che'i dbu rgyan dang /
NK015(ba)011:583: sham thabs la sogs pa rgyan chen po rnams kyis brgyan par bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:584: de ni dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK015(ba)011:585: yongs su rdzogs pa'i gsum pa byin gyi rlabs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)011:586: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:588: bdag gi dbu'i dung khang gi nang du zla ba'i dal gyi steng du /
NK015(ba)011:589: sku rdo rje sku mdog dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu can /
NK015(ba)011:590: de'i thugs kar 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:591: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aak+ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:593: bdag gi lce thog tu pad+ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)011:594: gsung rdo rje sku mdog dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu can /
NK015(ba)011:595: de'i thugs kar pad+ma am gis mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:596: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:598: bdag gi thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK015(ba)011:599: thugs rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag /
NK015(ba)011:600: rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK015(ba)011:601: de'i thugs kar rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:602: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa nu r+aa ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:604: lte ba rin chen zur brgyad kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)011:605: chags pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ser po rin po che dang dril bu can /
NK015(ba)011:606: de'i thugs kar rin po che s+w+aas mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:607: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa puts+tsha badz+ra swa b+ha wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)011:609: gsang gnas su chos 'byung gru gsum gyi steng du
NK015(ba)011:610: mchod pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ljang ku ral gri
NK015(ba)011:612: de'i thugs kar ral gri ham gis mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:613: lha de dag gi thugs kar ye shes sems dpa'
NK015(ba)011:614: rang 'dra ba re re la gdan ni rigs lnga
NK015(ba)011:615: yab yum dang / sems dpa' yab yum kun bzang yab yum la nyi zla pad+ma gsum brtsegs /
NK015(ba)011:616: thub drug dang bzang mo la pad+ma /
NK015(ba)011:617: sgo ba bzhi la nyi ma'o //
NK015(ba)011:618: lha de dag gi thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du thugs phyag mtshan la /
NK015(ba)011:619: gsung yig 'bru'i mtshan pa la lugs gnyis te /
NK015(ba)011:620: bskyed pa'i sa bon la +aa li dang /
NK015(ba)011:621: sngags kyi yi ge dang pos mtshan pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)011:622: 'dir phyag len la thub drug ma gtogs pa sngags kyi yi ge dang pos mtshan la /
NK015(ba)011:623: thub drug la kre la sogs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:624: sgo ba bzhi la h'u bzhi /
NK015(ba)011:625: yum la dza h'u bam ho bzhis mtshan pa de'i mtha' bskor du /
NK015(ba)011:626: rang gi sngags kyis bskor ba'o //
NK015(ba)011:627: lha de dag gi thugs kar thugs ye shes sems dpa' rang dang 'dra ba re re bsgom /
NK015(ba)011:628: de'i thugs kar thugs phyag mtshan la sngar gyi yi ge rnams kyis mtshan par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)011:629: de'i mtha' bskor du rang rang gi sngags kyis 'khor bar bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)011:630: de nas bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor phyogs bcu nas spyan drangs te bstims pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:631: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:632: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sh+ya ho /
NK015(ba)011:637: de dag ni byin gyis rlabs pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK015(ba)011:638: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhis bstan pa'i tha ma /
NK015(ba)011:639: mchod pa'i cho 'phrul la don rnam pa dgu ste /
NK015(ba)011:641: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:643: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:646: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:647: rmad du byung ba gtor ma bdud rtsi lnga'i mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:649: glu ye shes kyi mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:651: de nas yang bstod pa bya /
NK015(ba)011:653: de nas lhag ma'i cho ga bya /
NK015(ba)011:656: bla ma shar ba chen po spobs pa mtha' yas kyis sbyar ba'o //
NK015(ba)011:658: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)011:659: mngon par rtogs pa 'di la don gsum ste /
NK015(ba)011:660: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga dang /
NK015(ba)011:661: ting nge 'dzin bzhis mngon par rtogs pa'i gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:662: dngos grub blang zhing rjes kyi cho ga bya ba'o //
NK015(ba)011:663: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga la gsum ste /
NK015(ba)011:665: phyi'i cho ga bya zhing mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:666: bden pa gnyis kyi tshul gyis byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:667: mngon par rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhi ste /
NK015(ba)011:671: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK015(ba)011:673: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas bskyed pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:675: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul bstan pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:677: sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas byin gyis brlabs shing mchod pa'i cho 'phrul bstan te /
NK015(ba)011:681: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:682: phyag 'tshal bar bya ba'i phyir bstod pa bya ba dang /
NK015(ba)011:686: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:687: se gol bsnol ma gtogs shing /
NK015(ba)011:688: me long g.ya' dag pa la gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar /
NK015(ba)011:689: chos sku la gzugs skur bzhengs nas byon ma rag par bsam la /
NK015(ba)011:691: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku //
NK015(ba)011:692: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK015(ba)011:693: thugs rjes ngang can chos sku dag pa las //
NK015(ba)011:694: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)011:695: badz+ra sa man dza h'u dza /
NK015(ba)011:696: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:697: ho yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK015(ba)011:698: nam mkha' bzhin la dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK015(ba)011:699: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par rol pa'i klong //
NK015(ba)011:700: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK015(ba)011:701: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thugs dam dbyings kyi lha //
NK015(ba)011:702: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol pa chen po'i sku //
NK015(ba)011:703: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK015(ba)011:704: thabs kyis ma rmongs bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK015(ba)011:705: ye shes sgyu ma rnam par rol pa'i sku //
NK015(ba)011:706: thugs rje sprul pa mang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK015(ba)011:707: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK015(ba)011:708: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa gshegs su gsol //
NK015(ba)011:709: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NK015(ba)011:710: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka tri sh+ya ho /
NK015(ba)011:713: dza h'u bam ho a gats+tsha ya /
NK015(ba)011:714: a gats+tsha ya h'u dzah zhes pho brang dang nye
NK015(ba)011:715: bar mdun du byon par bsgom la brten par bzhugs
NK015(ba)011:717: h'u bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK015(ba)011:718: thugs rje chen po byon pa legs //
NK015(ba)011:719: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK015(ba)011:720: dgyes shing brten par bzhugs su gsol //
NK015(ba)011:721: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK015(ba)011:724: zhes pas dbyer med par bstim mo /
NK015(ba)011:727: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK015(ba)011:728: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK015(ba)011:729: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK015(ba)011:730: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs ho //
NK015(ba)011:731: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK015(ba)011:732: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK015(ba)011:733: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK015(ba)011:734: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che ho //
NK015(ba)011:735: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK015(ba)011:736: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK015(ba)011:737: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang /
NK015(ba)011:739: / 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che ho //
NK015(ba)011:740: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK015(ba)011:741: mtha' yas kun tu sna tshogs 'phro //
NK015(ba)011:742: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK015(ba)011:743: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po ho //

NK015(ba)011:776: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni /

NK015(ba)011:790: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK015(ba)011:791: lha dang lha mo'i rdul snyed kyis //
NK015(ba)011:792: bro gar la sogs bsam yas pa //
NK015(ba)011:793: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK015(ba)011:794: bla ma rnams dang dkon mchog gsum //
NK015(ba)011:796: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni //
NK015(ba)011:797: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK015(ba)011:798: dbang po'i yul du gang gyur ba //
NK015(ba)011:799: thabs dang shes rab ldan 'gyur zhing //
NK015(ba)011:800: mnyam pa'i ngang nyid rtog gsal na //

NK015(ba)011:802: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK015(ba)011:803: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
NK015(ba)011:805: bsgul bskyod thams cad phyag rgya yin /
NK015(ba)011:807: / 'di ni spyi rgya chen po ste //
NK015(ba)011:808: bla med chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK015(ba)011:809: gsung ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK015(ba)011:811: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK015(ba)011:812: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK015(ba)011:813: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa la //
NK015(ba)011:814: sbyor ba'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK015(ba)011:815: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te /

NK015(ba)011:818: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK015(ba)011:819: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya /

NK015(ba)011:937: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten /
NK015(ba)011:939: / 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta ba ni //

NK015(ba)011:942: rdo rje rin chen rna ltag tu //
NK015(ba)011:943: me tog snod bcas 'dzin pa la /
NK015(ba)011:945: / 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta ba ni //
NK015(ba)011:946: me tog phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK015(ba)011:948: rdo rje snye ma'i thugs ka nas //
NK015(ba)011:949: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten /

NK015(ba)011:955: rdo rje sems dpa' las la 'khril /

NK015(ba)011:959: pam d+ai pa su ki n+ai /
NK015(ba)011:960: rdo rje ut+pala thugs ka nas //
NK015(ba)011:961: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten /
NK015(ba)011:965: / 'jam dpal gyis ni phyag rgya yin //
NK015(ba)011:966: m+aum sh+r+ai a r+aam g+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:967: rin chen dbyug pa thugs ka nas //
NK015(ba)011:968: rdo rjes myug par byed pa dang /
NK015(ba)011:971: dri yi phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK015(ba)011:973: r+n+ri mgo gdengs ba gshed po ste //
NK015(ba)011:975: 'dzum gnyis bkug pa lcags kyu'i rgya //
NK015(ba)011:976: badz+ra d+h+aa ro ma h+aa kro te shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:977: rdo rje rnon po stobs chen rgya //

NK015(ba)011:984: pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro ti shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:985: rgya gram gnon pa 'khyil pa'i rgya //
NK015(ba)011:988: karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro ti shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:989: pi wam lan pa lha'i rgya /
NK015(ba)011:991: mi ni sreg par 'dzin pa ste /
NK015(ba)011:992: mu ne h'u t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)011:993: lha min phyag rgya go cha yin //
NK015(ba)011:995: chos kyi 'khor lo byol song rgya //
NK015(ba)011:997: za ma tog ni yi dwags rgya //
NK015(ba)011:999: me chu gnyis ni dmyal ba'i rgya //
NK015(ba)011:1001: yab kyi spyi rgya kun bzang gis //
NK015(ba)011:1003: yum gyi spyi rgya bzang mor bshad //
NK015(ba)011:1004: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta /
NK015(ba)011:1005: yang na kun bzang yab yum gyis //
NK015(ba)011:1006: rdo rje thal mo nyid du bshad //
NK015(ba)011:1011: dgyes pas rdo rje bsor mdzad nas //
NK015(ba)011:1012: byang chub sems sprin dbab tu gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1013: rdo rje bsor ba'i dga' mchog 'di /
NK015(ba)011:1017: rdo rje 'dzin mar ldan las byung //
NK015(ba)011:1018: shes rab dbyings ma yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK015(ba)011:1019: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus rab bkod de //
NK015(ba)011:1020: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i sbyor mchod kyis //
NK015(ba)011:1021: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs la mchod par 'bul //
NK015(ba)011:1022: badz+ra pra be sha ya a la la ho /
NK015(ba)011:1024: bdag gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham gis snod
NK015(ba)011:1025: bcud kyi sems can thams cad sbyang ste sems can
NK015(ba)011:1026: thams cad a dkar por gyur nas bdag gi thugs
NK015(ba)011:1028: de la mchod sbyin dam pa ni //
NK015(ba)011:1029: thog mar bdag nyid rtog goms bsgral //
NK015(ba)011:1030: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK015(ba)011:1031: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK015(ba)011:1032: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK015(ba)011:1033: zhing gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1034: nyi zla'i dkyil du mkhas pas bzhag /
NK015(ba)011:1035: nga rgyal lag gis 'du byed bsgom //
NK015(ba)011:1036: h'u du gyur nas rnam par dag /
NK015(ba)011:1037: dbyings su thim nas phyag rgyar 'bar //
NK015(ba)011:1039: gtsug tu rnam par rgyal ba bsgom //
NK015(ba)011:1040: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK015(ba)011:1041: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK015(ba)011:1042: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK015(ba)011:1043: de la byas pa rdul tsam med //
NK015(ba)011:1045: ho rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK015(ba)011:1046: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK015(ba)011:1047: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga'i dngos //
NK015(ba)011:1048: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK015(ba)011:1049: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK015(ba)011:1050: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK015(ba)011:1051: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK015(ba)011:1052: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen dang //

NK015(ba)011:1054: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen dang //

NK015(ba)011:1058: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK015(ba)011:1059: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //

NK015(ba)011:1061: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //

NK015(ba)011:1069: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //

NK015(ba)011:1085: phyi nang bdud tshogs thams cad 'dul mdzad pa //
NK015(ba)011:1086: gnas yul ro lang rdo rje bcing bsdoms 'beb //
NK015(ba)011:1087: sprul pa'i sgo skyong khro rgyal yab yum la //
NK015(ba)011:1088: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)011:1089: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ho /
NK015(ba)011:1090: dug lnga ma spangs dug gsum rnam dag pa'i //
NK015(ba)011:1091: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK015(ba)011:1092: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)011:1093: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ho /
NK015(ba)011:1094: tshe rabs sngon nas las kyis 'phro 'thud pa'i //
NK015(ba)011:1095: mched dang lcam dral karma ging la sogs //
NK015(ba)011:1096: rdo rje lcam dral ma lus 'khor bcas la //
NK015(ba)011:1097: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK015(ba)011:1098: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ho /
NK015(ba)011:1099: rmad du byung ba gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:1100: h'u gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK015(ba)011:1101: gzugs mdzes spyod pas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK015(ba)011:1102: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)011:1103: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim //

NK015(ba)011:1106: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NK015(ba)011:1108: sgra'i lha mo snyan la thim //
NK015(ba)011:1110: dri ni lag gnyis spos bsnams te //
NK015(ba)011:1111: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa 'phro //
NK015(ba)011:1112: kun tu tshim byed dri bsrung ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1113: dri'i lha mo shangs la thim //
NK015(ba)011:1115: ro ni lag gnyis snod bsnams te //
NK015(ba)011:1116: bcud ldan ro la mchog lnga brgyar 'phro //
NK015(ba)011:1117: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)011:1118: ro'i lha mo ljags la thim /
NK015(ba)011:1120: rig ni rdo rje yang 'khyud ma //

NK015(ba)011:1122: gzugs mdzes spyod pa phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK015(ba)011:1123: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //

NK015(ba)011:1128: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK015(ba)011:1129: chos kyi lha mo thugs kar thim //

NK015(ba)011:1136: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK015(ba)011:1137: steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo dkar ser dmar ljang
NK015(ba)011:1138: rnams kyis spyan shangs thugs ka sku lus la thim
NK015(ba)011:1139: / de nas bar bdud rtsi rgya mtsho lha rnams
NK015(ba)011:1140: kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gur gyur nas gsol bar
NK015(ba)011:1141: / bsam la / rang gi sngags la kh+aa hi btags pa 'bul lo //
NK015(ba)011:1143: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK015(ba)011:1145: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK015(ba)011:1150: glu tshigs sgra'i phyag rgya yis //
NK015(ba)011:1151: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK015(ba)011:1152: rgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis /
NK015(ba)011:1155: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK015(ba)011:1156: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK015(ba)011:1157: a li k+ai li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK015(ba)011:1160: zhi ba'i glu drug nyid dam /
NK015(ba)011:1161: thabs kyi zhags pa nas byung ba'i glu brgyad kyis bstod do //
NK015(ba)011:1163: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK015(ba)011:1164: bla med lha dang lha mo yis //
NK015(ba)011:1165: grub pa'i byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK015(ba)011:1166: sems dpa' bcu drug rigs kyi gtso //
NK015(ba)011:1167: sems ma bcu drug rigs kyi yum //
NK015(ba)011:1168: mthu chen khro bo khro mo dang //
NK015(ba)011:1169: pho nya 'jig rten skyongs bar ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1170: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni /
NK015(ba)011:1172: / 'jig rten thams cad ma lus kun //
NK015(ba)011:1173: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK015(ba)011:1174: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK015(ba)011:1175: dpa' bo chen po mthu ldan rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1176: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK015(ba)011:1177: bdag gis lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1178: grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1179: khams gsum zhing du sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)011:1180: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)011:1181: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)011:1182: cir yang sprul ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)011:1184: de nas dam blang ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:1185: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya bca' la /
NK015(ba)011:1186: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK015(ba)011:1187: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK015(ba)011:1188: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas rnams /
NK015(ba)011:1190: / 'gro la phan pa'i don du spyad //
NK015(ba)011:1191: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK015(ba)011:1192: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK015(ba)011:1193: srog gi phyir yang mo gtong na //
NK015(ba)011:1194: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlobs shig /
NK015(ba)011:1201: snying kha gnas gsum du gtug go //
NK015(ba)011:1202: rjes kyi cho ga bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:1205: thun mtshams kyi rnal 'byor rnams te /
NK015(ba)011:1206: dang po lhag ma bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)011:1207: bdag gi thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal po byung ste /
NK015(ba)011:1208: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa drug rang dbang med par spyan drangs nas /
NK015(ba)011:1209: bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga'i 'khor du phyogs bzhir brgyad brgyad zur bzhir bzhi bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)011:1210: de nas lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK015(ba)011:1228: dak+ki ni h+r+ai da ya h'u phata /
NK015(ba)011:1230: so so'i srog snying phul nas /
NK015(ba)011:1231: zhing tshal ba'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK015(ba)011:1236: mtshams rnams kyang tshul de ltar du bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:1237: kun kyang lag na gri gug dang /
NK015(ba)011:1239: rus pa'i rgyan gyis grub pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:1242: pra tits+tsha e mam b+ha ling+ta h'u phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)011:1244: pra tits+tsha e mam b+ha ling+ta phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)011:1246: t+r+aam sarba rat+na d+aak+ka d+aak+ki ni /
NK015(ba)011:1247: pra tits+tsha e mam b+ha ling+ta t+r+aam phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)011:1249: h+r+aihsarba pad+ma d+aak+ka d+aak+ki ni h+r+aihphatahpra tits+tsha e mam b+ha ling+ta h+r+aihphata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)011:1251: ha sarba karma d+aak+ka d+aak+ki ni pra tits+tsha /
NK015(ba)011:1252: e mam b+ha ling+ta ha phata kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)011:1255: / 'di rnams rgyas par na so so'i grangs dang tshad du bazla'o //
NK015(ba)011:1256: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ljags kyi rtse mo las /
NK015(ba)011:1258: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi zhal du thim par bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:1260: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur nas /
NK015(ba)011:1261: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis gsol bar sgom pa ni bdud rtsi'i dgongs pa'o //
NK015(ba)011:1262: dug gsum gyi sha khrag tu gyur nas /
NK015(ba)011:1263: mkha' 'gro ma rnams la bstab pa ni /
NK015(ba)011:1265: de nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi cag ge nyan par bsgom zhing /
NK015(ba)011:1266: rdo rje dril bu thogs la 'di skad do //
NK015(ba)011:1267: h'u bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK015(ba)011:1268: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK015(ba)011:1269: mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1270: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1271: yi dwags stan la yang dag bzhugs //
NK015(ba)011:1273: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1274: gdug pa'i sems kyis bsdig byed cing //
NK015(ba)011:1275: sha khrag dang ni rgyu ma dang //
NK015(ba)011:1276: rkang dang tshil bu za spyod rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1277: za bar byed cing 'dren par byed //
NK015(ba)011:1278: gsod par byed cing phrog par byed //
NK015(ba)011:1279: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1280: shar gyi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1282: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1284: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1285: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1286: dpal dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1287: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1288: gzi brjid che dang 'bar byed ma /
NK015(ba)011:1290: / 'dzem byed ma dang bong bu'i mgo //
NK015(ba)011:1291: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1292: lho'i phyogs nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1294: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1295: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1296: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1297: bde ba can gyi 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1298: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1299: chags chen ma dang chags bral ma /
NK015(ba)011:1302: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1303: nub kyi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1305: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1307: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1308: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1309: rnam par dag po'i 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1310: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //

NK015(ba)011:1313: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1314: byang gi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1316: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1318: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1319: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1320: sha chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1321: bya rog gdong ni mig 'phrul can /
NK015(ba)011:1324: shar lho nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1325: lag par gri dang khrag gzhong thogs //
NK015(ba)011:1326: mchog tu sha dang khrag la dgyes //
NK015(ba)011:1327: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1328: shar lho'i mtshams nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1330: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1332: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1333: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1334: keng rus spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1335: bzhad dang 'ug pa gdong ring ma //
NK015(ba)011:1336: khros pa khyi dang phag gi gdong //
NK015(ba)011:1337: lho nub nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1339: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1340: lho nub mtshams nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1342: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1344: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1345: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1346: rak+ta khrag gi rba klong nas //
NK015(ba)011:1347: rnga mong bong bu'i gdung 'dzin te //
NK015(ba)011:1348: khros pas ra dang byi la'i gdong //
NK015(ba)011:1349: nub byang nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1350: rgyu ma'i mgo nas za bar byed //
NK015(ba)011:1351: kun kyang rang gi lag cha ldan //
NK015(ba)011:1352: nub byang mtshams nas gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1354: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1356: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1357: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1358: thal chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK015(ba)011:1359: keng rus dkar po 'dzin pa ste //
NK015(ba)011:1360: khros pas rus pa'i phreng ba klub //
NK015(ba)011:1361: byang shar nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1362: phan tshun 'thab cing rtsod par byed /
NK015(ba)011:1364: / 'jigs byed drag po'i mche ba can //
NK015(ba)011:1365: lce spyang gi ni 'khor gyis bskor //
NK015(ba)011:1366: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan /
NK015(ba)011:1368: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1370: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1371: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1372: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK015(ba)011:1376: shar gyi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK015(ba)011:1377: rdo rje mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK015(ba)011:1378: srin po bum rna gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1381: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan /
NK015(ba)011:1383: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1385: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1386: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1387: lho'i phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK015(ba)011:1388: rin chen mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK015(ba)011:1389: rdo rje dus mtshan gshegs su gsol /
NK015(ba)011:1392: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan /
NK015(ba)011:1394: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1396: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1397: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1398: nub kyi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK015(ba)011:1400: rdo rje dus kyi 'khor lo yang /
NK015(ba)011:1403: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan /
NK015(ba)011:1405: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1407: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1408: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1409: byang gi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK015(ba)011:1410: las kyi rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma //
NK015(ba)011:1411: rdo rje lang ka mgrin bcu yang //
NK015(ba)011:1412: gnod sbyin bye ba 'bum dang bcas //
NK015(ba)011:1413: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan /
NK015(ba)011:1415: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)011:1417: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrub //
NK015(ba)011:1418: las bcol phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK015(ba)011:1419: mkha' 'gro pho mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK015(ba)011:1420: sngon tshe bcom ldan rigs lnga yis //
NK015(ba)011:1421: pho rnams btul te gdan du bting //
NK015(ba)011:1422: mo rnams btul te mdza' mor byas //
NK015(ba)011:1423: so so'i dam tshig bgos pa bzhin //
NK015(ba)011:1424: bdag kyang rgyal ba'i bstan bsrung na //
NK015(ba)011:1425: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK015(ba)011:1426: bar du gcod pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK015(ba)011:1427: myur du sgrol la med par mdzod //
NK015(ba)011:1428: bdud 'dul mthu dang skal ldan tshe //
NK015(ba)011:1429: mdzod ldan nor dang 'khor rnams kyis //
NK015(ba)011:1430: dngos grub dam pa stsal du stsol //
NK015(ba)011:1432: mkha' 'gro ma rnams so so'i rigs la bsdu /
NK015(ba)011:1435: slar skad cig gis rdo rje sems dpa'i skur bskyed /
NK015(ba)011:1438: spyod lam gyi bya ba rnams bya'o //
NK015(ba)011:1443: de thub drug dang kun bzang yab yum la /
NK015(ba)011:1444: de rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la /
NK015(ba)011:1445: de rigs bzhi yab yum la /
NK015(ba)011:1447: de rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK015(ba)011:1455: de mi dmigs pa la bzhag go //
NK015(ba)011:1456: de'i ngang la sngags brjod pas /
NK015(ba)011:1457: rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK015(ba)011:1458: phyag mtshan dang rgyan med pa'o //
